body:
Just wondering if there had been any progress on the issues currently being experienced on the OCE lobbies?

Was advised on Twitter the problem was known and being looked at, and here would be the best place to open up communication on the issue. Only lobby not currently experiencing it is the Custom Lobby, which I believe is Local? My assumption would be server side, after having several people repair clients and still experiencing it - And that every person apart of the lobby sees different results of the bug (some don't see players/role selections/queueing/game invites etcetc).

Sucky timing for it to happen on Vic Public Holiday.
 {{sticker:zombie-nunu-tears}} 


Thanks for your hard work.
{{sticker:katarina-love}}
